	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Repro steps:&#xD;&#xA;1. Start the game.&#xD;&#xA;2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;3. goto -625.75, 14.74, 354.75&#xD;&#xA;4. Talk with Elder Brithvar, convince him you are not a true soul (deception roll) and accept to help him.&#xD;&#xA;5. CTRL-Shift-K the Scrying eye.&#xD;&#xA;6. Destroy the rubbles holding Nere captive.&#xD;&#xA;7. Side with Nere in the mutiny (let Thrinn be killed) but resolve the combat by killing Nere and the rebels.&#xD;&#xA;8. Walk back to the main room, dialog should start afterward. " />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="270" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Player has sided with Nere, but Nere and Thrinn are dead by the time combat is over. In that case, a duergar initiates dialogue and tells you his plans and you get to decide the gnomes' fate." />
